route.name: Buller Stirling Showcase
route.about:
Trail Score: Black

360-degree views from Sterling including back to Buller Resort; nearby 500 year old snowgum; big views from multiple other high vantage points en route across to eastern Alps including nearly every other iconic peak in the Victorian Alps wilderness; huts including Bluff Spur and Geelong Grammar; sheer variety of terrain; running Stonefly (iconic MTB trail); wild flowers of Sterling plains.
